# Flutter Button styleFrom() Cheat Sheet

## Color Related

backgroundColor
→ Button-এর background color

```dart
backgroundColor: Colors.blue
```

foregroundColor
→ Text/Icon color

```dart
foregroundColor: Colors.white
```

disabledBackgroundColor
→ Button disabled হলে background color

```dart
disabledBackgroundColor: Colors.grey
```

disabledForegroundColor
→ Disabled text/icon color

```dart
disabledForegroundColor: Colors.black
```

shadowColor
→ Shadow color

```dart
shadowColor: Colors.black
```

surfaceTintColor
→ Material 3 tint effect

```dart
surfaceTintColor: Colors.blue
```

---

## Interaction Effects

hoverColor
→ Mouse hover করলে

```dart
hoverColor: Colors.purple
```

focusColor
→ Keyboard focus পেলে

```dart
focusColor: Colors.green
```

highlightColor
→ Press করে ধরে রাখলে

```dart
highlightColor: Colors.orange
```

overlayColor
→ Hover + Focus + Press effect

```dart
overlayColor:
  MaterialStatePropertyAll(Colors.red)
```

---

## Size Related

minimumSize
→ Minimum size

```dart
minimumSize: Size(60, 40)
```

fixedSize
→ Fixed size

```dart
fixedSize: Size(120, 50)
```

maximumSize
→ Maximum size

```dart
maximumSize: Size(200, 80)
```

---

## Spacing

padding
→ Inner spacing

```dart
padding: EdgeInsets.all(15)
```

---

## Border & Shape

shape
→ Button shape

```dart
shape: RoundedRectangleBorder(
  borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(15),
)
```

Circle Button

```dart
shape: CircleBorder()
```

side
→ Border

```dart
side: BorderSide(
  color: Colors.red,
  width: 2,
)
```

---

## Shadow

elevation
→ Shadow depth

```dart
elevation: 10
```

---

## Mouse

mouseCursor
→ Mouse pointer style

```dart
mouseCursor: SystemMouseCursors.click
```

---

## IconButton Only

iconSize
→ Icon size

```dart
iconSize: 30
```

---

# সবচেয়ে বেশি ব্যবহৃত Property

backgroundColor
